meanings.definition: A primitive mesenchymal cell that gives rise to blood vessels and blood cells.
meanings.english_definition: A primitive mesenchymal cell that gives rise to blood vessels and blood cells.

etymology.value: From desmo- (Greek δεσμός 'bond, band') + hemo- (Greek αἷμα 'blood') + -blast (Greek βλαστός 'bud, sprout').
